snippet.textDisplay:
Review: I Do It - Lil Wayne feat. Big Sean & Lil Baby
The intro I love, but the cussing and the first verse is the most decent thing I have ever seen. This beat but oh Lil Baby ruins this in to time. Omg his voice is awful. The chorus is ok, I guess? The beat SLAPS though, Big Sean pretty good, but that “BLAC BLAC BLAC” made me think 6ix9ine is coming. Then some random stuff, and the chorus again. This isn’t really flowed we-LIL BABY AGAIN? Oh shit this is weird. The ending is good. A 7/10, and reminder, fuck you, Lil Baby
snippet.textOriginal:
Review: I Do It - Lil Wayne feat. Big Sean & Lil Baby
The intro I love, but the cussing and the first verse is the most decent thing I have ever seen. This beat but oh Lil Baby ruins this in to time. Omg his voice is awful. The chorus is ok, I guess? The beat SLAPS though, Big Sean pretty good, but that “BLAC BLAC BLAC” made me think 6ix9ine is coming. Then some random stuff, and the chorus again. This isn’t really flowed we-LIL BABY AGAIN?
